http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Vijayawada/Geotagging-of-borewells-for-effective-monitoring/article14600100.ece

 For effective monitoring, the officials have taken up geotagging of nearly 1.61 lakh agricultural borewells spread over all parts of the Nellore district with special focus on the upland mandals.Already, 75,000 borewells have been tagged with steps being taken to complete the overall process as early as possible. The process is expected to provide updated and accurate information about the functioning of active borewells in rural areas.